title: Looking for a club to Duo Q
body:
Hey I'm looking for people to Duo Q.
I'm a Platinum support main and my IGN is MasochistSupMain.

replies.body: I'm a D5 ADC main that goes by the IGN of Corvo Attano, I own the Oceanic ADC club tag so it's likely you'll find some duos there, contact me if you're interested.
